Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.53,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister! This is the best deal \Nyou're going to find in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.50,JoJo-main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what the other guy said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.78,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then as a bonus, I'll give \Nyou a tour of the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:17.87,JoJo-main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.35,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:20.73,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:21.72,JoJo-main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.06,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,My bag is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:23.83,JoJo-main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.29,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.11,JoJo-main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,So, any changes lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.56,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:31.67,JoJo-main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.02,JoJo-main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.96,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:37.93,JoJo-main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:41.90,JoJo-main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but this is all I have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.39,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is all I can sell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.87,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Naples: a city located in southern Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:00.43,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's a famous tourist spot so beautiful that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:04.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,people say you should see it \Nat least once before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:06.39,JoJo-main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.46,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How do you get to Santa Chiara?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:14.36,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to get to Santa Chiara, go straight, \Nand then, at the first light—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.01,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:17.57,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.02,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:19.85,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so mu—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:21.14,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:22.65,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.77,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.77,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.44,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:36.70,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:37.43,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.19,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.33,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:44.64,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.71,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wasn't that guy super cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.78,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I should've asked for a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.60,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Did those just come out of my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.35,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What? They probably just \Nlanded on it for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:57.73,JoJo-main,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.52,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let your guard down in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.15,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:14.37,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get a cone with a scoop of \Nchocolate and a scoop of pistachio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.63,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Make that two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:19.60,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:43.39,JoJo-EpTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(529,436)}Episodio 01   Golden Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.90,JoJo-top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How many times do I have to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.97,JoJo-top,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can't run your business \Nhere without a license?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.63,JoJo-top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Move your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:45.93,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.39,JoJo-top,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,You only moved one car length away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:50.37,JoJo-main,Creep,0000,0000,0000,,So, whaddya say? It's faster than lining up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.62,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.32,JoJo-main,driver,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you into the city real cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.36,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Really? How cheap?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.73,JoJo-main,Creep,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.59,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that you need to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:09.96,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the protection fees you owe me \Nbefore doing any more business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.62,JoJo-main,driver,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:14.02,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you need to pay \Nthe protection fees you owe me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.57,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,before doing any more business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.00,JoJo-main,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.19,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.76,JoJo-main,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.88,JoJo-main,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:33.06,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You should think more about your \Nfriendship with me than your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.71,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:37.36,JoJo-main,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one ignoring \Nyou to keep doing business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.23,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.03,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:46.28,JoJo-main,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Giorno! Giorno Giovanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:47.76,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:51.28,JoJo-main,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's been making a fortune lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.78,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:58.63,JoJo-main,Luda,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll deal with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.47,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.53,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run your business \Nhere without a license!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.60,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.41,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Buon giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.23,JoJo-main,Kochi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.67,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,That flight was so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.34,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,The air sure is different here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.65,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, time to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:26.62,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno Shiobana... That's an unusual name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.81,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,First, I need to get to my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.95,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to dump my luggage so I can \Nmove around a bit more freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:35.10,JoJo-main,Kochi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Where's the taxi pick-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.92,JoJo-main,Cop 1,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.02,JoJo-main,Cop 2,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? That trick is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.80,JoJo-main,Cop 2,0000,0000,0000,,This shouldn't be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.75,JoJo-main,Cop 1,0000,0000,0000,,How are you even doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.67,JoJo-main,Cop 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:50.66,JoJo-main,Cop 1,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you stuff your whole \Near into your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:53.60,JoJo-main,Cop 2,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was entertaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.56,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.76,JoJo-main,Cop 2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't attract too much attention \Nwith your job here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.43,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for a taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.56,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, n-not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.28,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.91,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just finishing up my part-time job and \Nabout to head home, so I'll make it cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.54,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,How about 180,000 lire to \Nget you into the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.67,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,180,000? That's... about 10,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.92,JoJo-main,Kochi,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.91,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The basic rate is about half that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:23.34,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you speak the language perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.08,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.82,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you used to live in Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:30.79,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just had Rohan-sensei make it \Nso I could speak... Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:33.35,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,M-More importantly, you're saying you'll drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.79,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're only in \Nmiddle school or high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.96,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,And I saw you give the \Nsecurity guys something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.50,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I saw some money. \NWhat's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.07,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. You don't need \Nto worry about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.20,JoJo-main,giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about for 10,000 lire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.50,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't even ask for a tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.11,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you into the \Ncity for exactly 10,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.94,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? 10,000 would be about... 500 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.04,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.31,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just wait at the taxi pick-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.58,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.74,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll really only charge 10,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.91,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.22,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll have to load your \Nluggage on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:09.55,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm not asking for a tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.77,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Put your luggage up front. \NYou can sit in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.00,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:22.15,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better not think of me as some \NJapanese tourist who's not used to traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.56,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Just get me to my hotel in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.32,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll get you there in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.78,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say... \NI'll get your empty luggage there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:38.70,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait... I didn't even get in yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.43,JoJo-main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.04,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.52,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:44.59,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.67,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Reverb Act 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:57.69,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.99,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to underestimate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.57,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,You can run if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.03,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as my luggage is safe, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.28,JoJo-main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! Giorno actually screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.17,JoJo-main,Cop 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he gets for trying to trick
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.96,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a Japanese tourist when he's \Nhalf Japanese himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:23.66,JoJo-main,Cop 2,0000,0000,0000,,Though people would never \Nbe able to tell he's Japanese,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:26.50,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with that hair color and a \Nname like Giorno Giovanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.05,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.50,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's gone! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.22,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.80,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it a Stand?! But that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.40,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Would one show up the \Nsecond I get to Italy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.66,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a Stand! The way that frog felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.54,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.55,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, how'd my suitcase disappear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.44,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't have any time to hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.79,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.88,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,This is only a hunch, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:10.49,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.80,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you some questions \Nabout that taxi driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.74,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.77,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Giorno Giovanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.82,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we're meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who I am, Giorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.00,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Leaky Eye Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.58,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:47.25,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,even after someone stabbed a knife deep \Ninto your face, you didn't stop fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.43,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.84,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,even though your wound has healed, \Nyour eye is always watering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.05,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you have a seat right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.98,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.30,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,It's tiring having to look up at you to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.80,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.50,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.43,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen?! Wow, you're just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:19.29,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Giorno, there are three "yous" \Nto remember in friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.58,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Three "yous," got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.89,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,The first one is you don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.93,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,The second one is you don't hold grudges.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.83,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,And the third is you respect the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.30,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good, right? Those are \Nthe three "yous" of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.13,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:40.09,sign_13775_184_Smack,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(183,1)}S{\c&H736BB7&}m{\c&HA869C6&}a{\c&H746AB5&}c{\c&H678EBA&}k
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.31,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one talking right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:40.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could ask \Nquestions, you dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:44.18,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you've been working \Npart-time around the airport...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.13,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,I, Leaky Eye Luca, haven't received
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,any of the gifts that you should've \Ngiven me out of respect yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:55.11,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect our \Nfriendship to last like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.92,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take a peek at your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.82,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:01.83,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I already paid my protection fees. \NI don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.81,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,To the security guards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.38,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:11.00,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? A photo of a family member?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.90,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the money! Show me your wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.01,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.30,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say the same thing twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.58,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I already paid, \Nso I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.64,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it a third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.36,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.08,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.28,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,It came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.45,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Smack it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.07,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,This frog has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.78,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't smack it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:48.62,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you an order, and I told \Nyou to pay me a protection fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.42,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to disobey both of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:55.84,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to tell me, Leaky Eye Luca, \N"no" to both of those things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.86,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,This is a living creature \Nthat has its own conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.72,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's thinking on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.43,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,You really shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:07.52,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You're... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.53,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I could never just smack it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.47,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! It's harmless as long \Nas you don't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.05,JoJo-main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.61,sign_16128_219_Whack,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(105,1)}Whack
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.19,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:25.91,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even that loyal to me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:32.31,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,It's just trying to protect itself. \NIt has its own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:43.10,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Any attack on it becomes an attack \Non oneself, and it's fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.01,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:49.98,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you not to make me say it a third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.77,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Making me say the same \Nthing over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.00,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.73,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,And I hate that because it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.67,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Totally useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.13,JoJo-flashback,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of this guy's skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:11.43,JoJo-flashback,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I want you to get a sample \Nof it and send it to me, Koichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.34,JoJo-flashback,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,so the Speedwagon Foundation \Ncan check its composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.96,JoJo-flashback,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Its composition? Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.87,JoJo-flashback,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,His father, who died, was a bit special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.76,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we want to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:26.43,JoJo-flashback,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,It can be thin. I just need \Nyou to get me a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.86,JoJo-flashback,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.18,JoJo-flashback,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.57,JoJo-flashback,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover all your expenses for this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:33.39,JoJo-flashback,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?! All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.61,JoJo-flashback,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:42.01,JoJo-flashback,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if this sounds rude, but this \Nguy sort of looks like you, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:48.92,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,The address on this picture \Nis somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.77,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,How careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.54,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:58.92,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No one around here is dumb enough \Nto try and steal their briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:03.09,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I guess this is a nice neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.04,JoJo-top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.50,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come in for a meal, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.80,JoJo-top,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to sit next to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.48,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:12.18,JoJo-top,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Giorno! Have some tea with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.54,JoJo-top,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wait, I'll pay for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.60,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.60,JoJo-top,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,No, me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.10,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I like being alone. Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.57,JoJo-main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.44,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.74,JoJo-main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.28,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:31.70,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Whose money is that?! \NAre you using my money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.69,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,You?! How'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:36.93,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my passport! \NWhere's my luggage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.17,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts me to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.54,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,but they're gone. \NI sold them off, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.17,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,So stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.34,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.15,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:54.22,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... So that wasn't \Na malfunction earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:58.12,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... he has the same \Nkind of powers as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.11,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:00.90,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:05.03,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.70,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Life, spring forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.04,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Bring forth new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.96,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just caught a glimpse of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.33,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Act 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.05,JoJo-main,Act3,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.16,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd be able to escape \N3 Freeze's range that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:35.35,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this one more time. \NDon't even think about coming after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:39.46,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I hate saying things twice \Nwhen I shouldn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.78,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's useless to say it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.29,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do things that are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.02,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Knock him down, Act 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:58.68,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The attack on the tree \Ncame back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:01.33,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I took something of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.84,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,but I can tell you held back \Nwhen you were trying to hit me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.72,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when I see what that damage has done to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.93,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:17.67,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.\NGiorno Giovanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:20.77,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.95,JoJo-Eyecatch3,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(152,1)}Giorno Giovanna
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.95,JoJo-Eyecatch2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(146,1)}Golden Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.41,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.40,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, it's me, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:43.76,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Koichi. Did you get to Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.82,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy you asked me to find! \NHaruno Shiobana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.72,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:52.25,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Where do I even begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.41,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I immediately ran into him at the airport...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.89,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,And, yes, it's safe to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.85,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.97,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,He goes by the name Giorno Giovanna in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.82,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned before that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.61,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Stand users are drawn to \Nother Stand users, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:10.37,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,We seriously met by coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:13.24,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's a student, but he \Nacts like a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.91,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He stole my money and my luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.40,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,And it appears his Stand's ability is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.38,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,returning his opponent's\Nattack right back at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.99,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:26.06,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you a hotel and wire you some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:30.21,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, his hair was blond, \Nunlike in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.80,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,After asking some people \Nwho knew him about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.89,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,they said that he didn't dye it. \NIt just suddenly turned that color.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Something about his dead father's genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.12,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Who's his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you and his father somehow related?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.03,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.13,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,who killed his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.54,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,His name is DIO Brando.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:58.70,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,DIO?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.12,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the one involved \Nwith the bow and arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:16:59.87,sign_2606_40_Glob,,0000,0000,0000,,Stab
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.80,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I found out this year that \NDIO may have had a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.00,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to find out for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:14.68,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,if Giorno Giovanna was really DIO's child, \Nand if he's somehow inherited his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:18.18,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't DIO's body belong \Nto the Joestar bloodline?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.99,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that his hair turned \Nblond may be a sign that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:26.27,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,the DIO blood in him, his Stand \Npower, recently awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.73,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,There might have been a trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:32.57,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,like a powerful Stand user being in that city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.20,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go near him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.77,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to take this further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.28,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.50,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Just one last question...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.82,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is he our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.21,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,Or is he a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.53,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.55,JoJo-main,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who actually met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,Jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What was your impression of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.32,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.47,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:06.04,JoJo-main,Koichi,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed like a very eloquent person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.24,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you drop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.16,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:27.71,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.37,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:37.59,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say you found a bag \Nwith 100,000 lire inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.98,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,would you take it to the authorities?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.22,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I'd totally take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.04,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:49.55,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,But what if I was a plainclothes \Npolice officer and saw you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:56.08,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give you half and have you \Nlook the other way... probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:01.16,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.91,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure that's actually what you'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.91,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're not kidding or bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:09.42,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell! You're telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:13.99,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,You see... I can tell if people \Nare telling the truth or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:16.37,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:19.38,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,You know how your skin gets \Nshiny when you sweat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.30,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:25.76,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll have an even better \Nidea if I taste your sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.85,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:34.84,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Leaky Eye Luca was found on the ground \Nnear the airport after having
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.17,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,his own spade buried in the back of his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:40.46,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rather serious injury. \NHe won't be regaining consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.84,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to find out who's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:49.00,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno Giovanna, no one knows why \NLeaky Eye Luca was at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:52.22,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,But the airport security guards
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:55.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,let me know that you were at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:59.66,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I figured I'd come see \Nyou and ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.05,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually a police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.50,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.90,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Luca's no ordinary crook. \NHe's a gang member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.02,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of reasons \Nhe might've been taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.95,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,He knew how to get people to hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:17.82,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not what his boss is thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.76,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,The boss feels like his name was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:22.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,personally tarnished since \None of his own was taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:27.28,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he told me to find out who \Ntook him out and settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.65,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:33.62,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you happen to run into \NLeaky Eye Luca at the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.09,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't know who you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:49.28,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're not sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.49,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.56,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That does it for my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.01,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have bothered you, Giorno Giovanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.48,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand was clenched the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.25,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's Luca's right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.97,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,He's unconscious anyway, so I just brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:26.14,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,This taste... is the taste of someone \Nwho's lying, Giorno Giovanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.35,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.85,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I said I was done with my questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:37.24,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,but the situation seems to have \Nchanged, Giorno Giovanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.30,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,You told me a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:46.99,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'm going to have to find \Nout why you lied to me, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.38,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:52.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to hit him, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.97,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Bruno Bucciarati.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.82,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:04.38,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your questioning has already \Nturned into torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.72,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well? This is a pretty \Ncreepy ability, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.16,JoJo-main,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.85,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Luca's fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.16,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:20.67,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaky Eye Luca was disposed of by our boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:23.78,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,He said that there's no point \Nin him living anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:27.07,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I took his fingers for torturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:27.07,JoJo-internal/narrator,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,It's happening again! What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:31.58,JoJo-internal/narrator,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,Is he also like that Japanese tourist?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:35.81,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Other than being able to tell if people \Nare lying or not, I can also do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:40.76,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I can put whatever I want in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:42.04,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.47,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I can even put that fire \Nextinguisher in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:50.29,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm afraid you'd die if I did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:55.81,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:58.73,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,You know who's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:00.59,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Were you told not to tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:04.44,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have you tell me who did Luca in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:09.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it... \NHe has a similar ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:13.75,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry up and tell me, \Nyour torture is just going to get worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:15.74,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno Giovanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:22.54,JoJo-internal/narrator,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:25.99,JoJo-internal/narrator,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:32.62,JoJo-internal/narrator,Giorno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to use Golden Wind \Nand dodge his attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.31,JoJo-NextTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1)}Episodio 02\N\NBucciarati Is Coming
